tags: xixilia: and the mother of the earth
summary: The Mother of Earth and all Life that resides within it. Character design assignment work. They say The Mother of Earth made the...
caption:
The Mother of Earth and all Life that resides within it.

Character design assignment work.

They say The Mother of Earth made the universe within a single orb that rests atop her staff so that she may forever protect it. They say that the human warrior Ba’nn flew to the edge of the orb to ask the Earth Mother for eternal life, when she declined his request he became enraged; shooting an arrow square into the middle of her face. She now protects her face by a mask that is said to haunt those who do not accept the fate of mortality.
A 300 year war devastated the Earth so much so that The Mother of Earth became weak and is now dying. Before all life on Earth ceases to exist she must find her spiritual successor. In that of the young nun, Xixilia.
